{
  "stem": "15577.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this was, by the way, my first-- my first meeting with so-called good and bad Poles.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I met there a woman whom we gave a lot of our clothes before we went to ghetto, because first of all, we couldn't take anything-- too much with us, as I told you before.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And secondly, we thought it won't take too much time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She was a friend of the family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She was a very good acquaintance with us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So when it's over, we will get it back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this woman was sitting there and was selling our clothes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when she saw me, she immediately recognized me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I recognized her too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And not that she didn't apologize, or-- her first sentence, she said-- her first reaction was, you're really-- you're really alive?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or something like this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was the first shock.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then on the street, you could hear from here and there, too many Jews were left.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I haven't got enough time to know how bad or how good the relations between Jews and Poles could be or will be after the war, because my decision was a very quick one.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as I said to you, this one accident was enough for me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The second one was when I met the drunk Russian soldiers, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] which I didn't like.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't like the atmosphere, so my decision was very, very final and very quick.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it didn't take too much time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went with my-- ah, in the meantime, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a cousin of mine, who-- I told you before that we were left with three cousins.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So one was killed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The second one came to Krakow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were [? all ?] in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
